  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Prospective study of sleep disordered breathing in a lung cancer screening cohort.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The proposed study is a prospective single arm study evaluating the prevalence of sleep
      disordered breathing in a cohort of lung cancer screening patients.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
